short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds a 'show images' button for displaying images on for printing images of the real estate ads

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
On realestate.com.au, domain.com.au, realcommercial.com.au, commercialrealestate.com.au when you press print it doesn't print all the images, just the first few.  This extension adds a button which shows all the images on one page.

realestate.com.au: You may have to press refresh on the browser to get the "show images" link to appear some times.
